						<ECUC-MODULE-DEF UUID="4f84b18c-14f8-4835-8851-c3489ab3399b">
							<SHORT-NAME>Eep</SHORT-NAME>
							<DESC>
								<L-2 L="EN">Configuration of the Eep (internal or external EEPROM driver) module.
Its multiplicity describes the number of EEPROM drivers present, so there will be one container for each EEPROM driver in the ECUC template. When no EEPROM driver is present then the multiplicity is 0.</L-2>
							</DESC>
							<CATEGORY>VENDOR_SPECIFIC_MODULE_DEFINITION</CATEGORY>
