											<SHORT-NAME>EepDeviceInformationRef</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Select a EEPROM device from the list or add a "custom" device in case none of the listed EEPROM devices are compatible. In the latter case it is necessary to enter the device's properties manually.</L-2>
											</DESC>
